### âœ… Set your variables

Click the [**Variables**](#variables) tab of the collection and provide the required values below:

| Variable        | Description               |
|-----------------|---------------------------|
| `base_url`      | Base URL of the API       |
| `client_id`     | OAuth client ID           |
| `client_secret` | OAuth client secret       |
| `username`      | API username              |
| `password`      | API password              |
| `idp`           | Identity provider name    |

---

Once these are set, you're all set â€” **authorization will be handled automatically**, and you can start testing the API right away.
